
# File: README

Code files proto_gui.py and gui.py need to be sorted.
They are both attempting to provide the same functionality:
... same functionality as cli.py but using tkinter.
Code file userinterface.py seems completely redundant:
... ../main.py does its job.

Ultimate goal is to have gui.py and cli.py providing
identical functionality to allow
import gui as ui
or
import cli as ui
Depending on which user interface one wishes to use.


